                *          Welcome to                 |
		|	Skill-Based Angband           *
		*       (Sangband)                    |
		| 	Version 0.8.5                 *
		+-------------------------------------+

	Hacked By: Alex Cutler, Andy Astrand
	Further Hacks By: Sean Marsh, Geoff Hill
	Skill Hacks By:  Chris Petit (petitc@rpi.edu) 
        Based On:  Angband 2.4
        Bug fixes: Sean Marsh, Geoff Hill, Charles Teague

Features:  Autorolling, Stat Modification, Targetting, Talents

News:  Skills have been better balanced---all require HIGH values to become
       extremely powerful.  Bowmaking skill added.  Druid magic replaces
       Ninjitsu magic.  Monsters become Afraid now.

Bugs:  Looking for them.  Report any bugs in Sangband to petitc@rpi.edu or
       post them on rec.games.roguelike.angband.


